data.metadata:
{"description":"Abstract ecosystem was where I met Ely. He joined with a bang, found his jam and started Max Abstracting everyone!

qualities based on my experiences with him

1. Top tier creator with market pulse - Versatile content with current focus on live streaming & videos. From interviews to walkthroughs, everything executed with top entertainment value. Understands and acts on meta.

4. Top Abstract mindshare - Almost always within the top 10 on any time frame for Abstract ecosystem.
